president reagan in an extraordinary 
questionandanswer session with soviet students said today that 
the united states would like nothing better than to help in the 
search for soviet soldiers missing in afghanistan 
the session covering topics as diverse as the plight of 
american indians to the twoterm restriction on american presidents 
