important it is to institutionalize change to put guarantees on 
reform 
and we have been talking together about one sad reminder of a 
divided world the berlin wall reagan said it is time to 
remove the barriers that keep people apart 
he told the students they are living in one of the most 
exciting hopeful times in soviet history it is a time when the 
first breath of freedom stirs the air and the heart beats to the 
accelerated rhythm of hope when the accumulated spiritual energies 
of a long silence yearn to break free 
he said we do not know what will be the conclusion of this 
