with finances 
the second special session starts wednesday and will cover all 
areas but education moore has proposed a nickelagallon gasoline 
tax increase to meet his proposed budget 
the third special session will be dedicated to education which 
takes up 72 percent of moores proposed 146billion budget the 
governor has threatened to revive several taxes which failed 
passage in the legislature previously no date has been set for the 
third session 
