<TEXT>
four worldclass trout rivers flow 
almost by the door of tiny rl winston rod co whose fly rods are 
recognized as among the best by hardcore equipment zealots 
money is no object for fly fishermen who seek out the winston 
factory in this western montana ranching town to test cast and 
maybe buy a 305 gossamertipped graphite wand or a 900 objet 
dart in bamboo 
its a fact that fishermen sometimes get starry looks when 
they first touch one of our rods its affection says tom 
morgan who bought the established san francisco rod maker in 1973 
and moved it to montana 
a rod communicates with you morgan says when you wiggle 
a winston rod it talks back to you with a good message 
he implied theres little back talk from a massproduced rod 
retailing for 1999 in a discount store 
our goal isnt to provide everyone with a winston rod and 
everyone cant afford them morgan says so the factory makes fly 
rods at an artistic snails pace of about 2000 a year 
morgan doubts his 59yearold company will ever produce more 
than 3000 rods a year 
morgan and the other winston employees dont blink an eye if an 
angler wants to cast half a dozen fly rods on the lawn across the 
street or buy one and substitute zebra wood for the standard 
walnut reel seat 
morgan who guided for 14 years and fishes all over the world 
might even accompany an eager angler to one of the nearby 
blueribbon trout rivers the big hole beaverhead ruby or 
jefferson 
he might even rig his favorite winston an 8foot 4weight 
graphite i like to fish small dry flies its just perfect for 
that morgan said 
winston has no fixed working days or hours for its five regular 
and seven parttime employees 
if one of the trout streams beckons they are free to go 
morgan says this provides them with the artistic freedom and 
inspiration they need to accomplish outstanding work 
winstons graphite rods are considered among the worlds best 
they are coated with a translucent kellygreen finish and guides 
are wrapped with matching green thread 
winston wont wind a rod with different color thread for a 
customer or do anything else that makes no aesthetic sense or 
technical sense morgan says 
there are 89 models of winston fly rods in 11 line sizes three 
actions three materials from 5 feet to 10 feet long 
once an angler buys a basic winston theres an enticing array 
of accouterments maybe a scrimshaw reel seat lovingly carved with 
a kingfisher german silver reel banks your name engraved on the 
rod 
our average customer has three to five of our rods and ive 
talked to people with a dozen morgan says 
almost all of winstons rods are graphite the bamboo operation 
supervised by partner glenn brackett may turn out only 75 rods 
this year 
tonkin cane for the beautifully finished classic rods comes 
from mainland china anglers may have to wait four to eight months 
for each custombuilt rod whose blemishfree bamboo strips are cut 
within a tolerance of onethousandth of an inch 
only 5 percent of the bamboo we get goes into our rods 
brackett says we reject the rest 
there are a lot of other good expensive fly rods on the market 
from companies like sage powell scott teton thomas amp thomas g 
loomis and orvis in fact winstons graphite rod blanks are made 
on its own tapers by g loomis a larger rod maker 
some fly rod companies offer futuristic materials 
superior tapers parabolic action the latest 
breakthrough materials morgan says a rods design is more 
important than the material it has to work for the type of 
fishing you do at winston we dont jump on every new material 
that comes along 
morgan says that a lot of the people who build fly rods dont 
fish enough you cant make great fly rods if you dont use them a 
lot 
he himself fishes a great deal in part because you almost 
always fish in a place where you can rebuild your spirit when im 
steelheading at times i almost wish a fish wouldnt come to my 
hook 
when it comes to hooking trout he believes in catching and 
releasing them for the marvelous sport they give us he says 
they deserve our best treatment you can turn the fish loose not 
like hunting when you kill the animal 
